OL,3,CLiverpool hotel owners have say on
OL,4,Cwhether to introduce tourist levy on
OL,5,Crooms
OL,7,FVisitors to Liverpool could soon see a
OL,8,F#2-a-night increase in the price of
OL,9,Fhotel rooms if a plan to introduce a
OL,10,F'tourist levy' in the city is accepted.
OL,12,FFrom today owners of 83 hotels in the
OL,13,Fcity can have their say on a proposal
OL,14,Fwhich aims to generate millions from
OL,15,Fthe local visitor economy.
