OL,3,CLiverpool hotel owners have say on
OL,4,Cwhether to introduce tourist levy on
OL,5,Crooms
OL,7,FBill Addy, CEO of Liverpool BID
OL,8,FCompany, says, "Major exhibitions and
OL,9,Fevents, like The Terracotta Warriors,
OL,10,Fcan attract a huge audience,
OL,11,Fgenerating income both for the visitor
OL,12,Feconomy, the tourism industry and
OL,13,Fhospitality. What we would love, as
OL,14,Fboth a city and a private sector, is
OL,15,Fto be able to support so that we can
OL,16,Fhold events like this much more
OL,17,Fregularly. The investment we are
OL,18,Fproposing could really turbo-charge
OL,19,Fthe city's economy".
