OL,3,CLiverpool hotel owners have say on
OL,4,Cwhether to introduce tourist levy on
OL,5,Crooms
OL,7,FIts a view echoed by others working in
OL,8,Fthe sector.
OL,10,FLaura Pye is the Chief Executive of
OL,11,FNational Museums Liverpool: "It would
OL,12,Fallow us to do some of the bigger
OL,13,Fstuff we want to do in the city.
OL,14,FLiverpool as a city is culturally
OL,15,Freally vibrant and has done fantastic
OL,16,Fthings in terms of the visitor economy
OL,17,Fbut you need to keep ahead of the
OL,18,Fgame. You have to keep investing to
OL,19,Fkeep Liverpool on the front foot as a
OL,20,Fgreat destination".
