OL,5,Crooms
OL,7,FIt also has support from some of those
OL,8,Fwho will be responsible for gathering
OL,9,Fthe levy.
OL,11,FLaura Delaney of The Municipal Hotel
OL,12,Fand Spa says that guests will be well
OL,13,Finformed about the extra charge:
OL,14,F"We'll have QR codes situated across
OL,15,Fthe hotels, they can find out a wee
OL,16,Fbit more about what it is and why it
OL,17,Fis there, and they'll be presented
OL,18,Fwith the bill at the end, it'll be
OL,19,Fadded to their bill"
