OL,3,CLiverpool hotel owners have say on
OL,4,Cwhether to introduce tourist levy on
OL,5,Crooms
OL,7,FHelen Roberts is the dual General
OL,8,FManager at Holliday Inn Express for
OL,9,FLiverpool and Manchester, and she says
OL,10,Fit is a positive move which the city
OL,11,Fneeds: "There's a lot that the BID
OL,12,Fdoes already in terms of improving the
OL,13,Fpublic realm, security and major
OL,14,Fevents, but Liverpool needs this to
OL,15,Fhelp it to thrive.
OL,17,F"Liverpool isn't the biggest city but
OL,18,Fit does need to compete on an
OL,19,Finternational stage. We have the same
OL,20,Fmodel in Manchester and there has been
OL,21,Flittle or no reaction from guests.
